{"type":"message","id":"4b9a3c6f","parentId":"dd54f187","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:02:24.148Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so the first extraction already worked and gave us the tapdsession cookie. But I'm concerned about missing other important cookies. Let me try a different approach: instead of copying the profile, let me use Playwright's built-in Chromium to start fresh and manually inject the tapdsession that we already have. Then navigate to TAPD and see what other cookies get generated.\n\nActually, for TAPD automation, the key question is: **does the `tapdsession` cookie alone work for API requests?** Let me check.\n\nLooking at the keepalive script and the bug creation script:\n- The bug creation uses Playwright with cookies loaded from tapd_cookies.json\n- The cookies are loaded via `context.addCookies(cookies)`\n- It then navigates to the TAPD bug creation page\n- If redirected to login, it throws \"TAPD session expired\"\n\nSo the key is: can we successfully navigate to TAPD without being redirected to login?\n\nLet me use the tapdsession cookie we already have and test it directly by launching a quick Playwright session.\n\nBut wait - there's a simpler approach. Let me re-copy the profile (without Chrome running this time) and run the extraction script again, this time waiting longer for the cookie setup.\n\nActually, let me try something even simpler. The `tapdsession` cookie is what we really need. Let me first kill all Chrome processes, re-copy the profile, and try again with a script that dumps ALL cookies (not just tapd.cn domain).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_VSh0Te5Y6nNWKiy9qjVt7524","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * 提取所有可见 cookie，不限制域名\n */\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst TEMP_PROFILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'temp_chrome_profile');\n\nasync function main() {\n  const context = await chromium.launchPersistentContext(TEMP_PROFILE, {\n    headless: false,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox'],\n  });\n\n  const page = context.pages()[0] || await context.newPage();\n\n  try {\n    // 先不导航，直接获取所有 cookie\n    let cookies = await context.cookies();\n    console.log(`Total cookies in context: ${cookies.length}`);\n    const domains = [...new Set(cookies.map(c => c.domain))].sort();\n    console.log('Domains:', domains.join(', '));\n\n    // 找 tapd / tencent / cloud 相关\n    const relevant = cookies.filter(c => {\n      const name = c.name.toLowerCase();\n      const domain = c.domain.toLowerCase();\n      return domain.includes('tapd') || domain.includes('qq.com') || domain.includes('tencent') ||\n             name.includes('tapd') || name.startsWith('t_') || name.startsWith('_t');\n    });\n    console.log(`\\nRelevant cookies: ${relevant.length}`);\n    relevant.forEach(c => console.log(`   ${c.name} (${c.domain}): ${c.value.substring(0, 40)}`));\n\n    if (relevant.length > 0) {\n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(relevant, null, 2), 'utf8');\n      console.log(`\\n✅ Saved ${relevant.length} cookies`);\n    }\n\n    // 然后导航到 TAPD 看看是否登录成功\n    console.log('\\n--- Navigating to TAPD ---');\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add', {\n      waitUntil: 'networkidle',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    console.log('URL:', page.url());\n\n    if (page.url().includes('login')) {\n      console.log('❌ Login required');\n    } else {\n      console.log('✅ Auto-login success!');\n      \n      // 重新获取 cookies（导航后可能有更多）\n      const finalCookies = await context.cookies();\n      const finalRelevant = finalCookies.filter(c => {\n        const n = c.name.toLowerCase();\n        const d = c.domain.toLowerCase();\n        return d.includes('tapd') || d.includes('qq.com') || d.includes('tencent') ||\n               n.includes('tapd') || n.startsWith('t_') || n.startsWith('_t');\n      });\n      console.log(`\\nFinal relevant cookies: ${finalRelevant.length}`);\n      finalRelevant.forEach(c => console.log(`   ${c.name} (${c.domain}): ${c.value.substring(0, 40)}`));\n      \n      fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(finalRelevant, null, 2), 'utf8');\n      console.log(`✅ Saved ${finalRelevant.length} cookies`);\n    }\n  } finally {\n    await context.close();\n    try { fs.rmSync(TEMP_PROFILE, { recursive: true, force: true }); } catch {}\n  }\n}\n\nmain().catch(err => {\n  console.error('FAILED:', err.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\extract_tapd_cookies_v4.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":141,"output":1194,"cacheRead":46208,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":47543,"cost":{"input":0.00001974,"output":0.00033432000000000004,"cacheRead":0.001293824,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.001647884}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779249731523,"responseId":"47202e7b-b281-4604-8b62-ddd65e521b68"}}
