{"type":"message","id":"b13aec82","parentId":"7a4a74ca","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:07:44.331Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK let me try a completely different and simpler approach:\n\n1. Copy the Chrome profile to temp\n2. Start Chrome with that temp profile + `--remote-debugging-port=9222`\n3. Navigate to TAPD manually? No, use Playwright to connect\n4. Extract cookies\n\nLet me try starting Chrome manually from command line with the copied profile.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_KlVMtvRge5Rt3grP0plj9082","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$tmpProfile = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_cp\"; if (Test-Path $tmpProfile) { Remove-Item -Recurse -Force $tmpProfile }; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $tmpProfile -Force | Out-Null; Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Local State\" -Destination \"$tmpProfile\\Local State\" -Force; robocopy \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\" \"$tmpProfile\\Default\" /E /R:2 /W:2 /NFL /NDL /NP 2>&1 | Out-String; Start-Process -FilePath \"C:\\Program Files\\Google\\Chrome\\Application\\chrome.exe\" -ArgumentList \"--user-data-dir=$tmpProfile\",\"--remote-debugging-port=9222\",\"--no-first-run\" -WindowStyle Normal; Start-Sleep -Seconds 5; Get-NetTCPConnection -LocalPort 9222 -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Select-Object LocalPort,State; Write-Host \"done\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":16,"output":395,"cacheRead":77824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":78235,"cost":{"input":0.00000224,"output":0.0001106,"cacheRead":0.0021790719999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0022919119999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779250060250,"responseId":"d0f83eef-57f8-471d-b7d0-3376bbb3caa7"}}
