{"type":"message","id":"af8664d2","parentId":"bdec1d69","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:11:33.265Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me use the same approach that worked before (temp profile copy + launchPersistentContext without channel: 'chrome'), because that first script actually succeeded in getting cookies. Let me check what the `launchPersistentContext` actually does - it launches Playwright's built-in Chromium, not system Chrome. And the first time it worked.\n\nWait, the first run used `launchPersistentContext(TEMP_PROFILE)` which would launch Playwright's Chromium with that user data directory. Chromium reads Chrome's cookie database. The cookies were... wait, were the cookie values actually the decrypted values, or were they empty?\n\nLet me re-check the first run:\n```\nFound 5 TAPD cookies\n✅ tapdsession: 17792496444cacb6af68c19f3f34be...\n```\n\nThe value `17792496444cacb6af68c19f3f34be...` looks like a real tapdsession value! And the domain was `.tapd.cn`. So `launchPersistentContext` with a profile copy DID work, and Chromium was able to read and decrypt the cookies.\n\nWhy? Because Playwright's bundled Chromium uses the SAME encryption libraries as Chrome to decrypt cookies. When it opens the profile and reads the cookie database, it can use the same DPAPI + AES-GCM to decrypt.\n\nThe first copy had a fresh session. But the subsequent copies had corrupted or empty cookie databases because of all the Chrome killing and restarting.\n\nLet me try the SAME approach that worked - use `launchPersistentContext` with a fresh profile copy and `headless: false` (headed mode).","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_8TOCfaBBn0B7OaJ1P9zV3717","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"$tmpProfile = \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_chrome_profile\"; if (Test-Path $tmpProfile) { Remove-Item -Recurse -Force $tmpProfile }; New-Item -ItemType Directory -Path $tmpProfile -Force | Out-Null; Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Local State\" -Destination \"$tmpProfile\\Local State\" -Force; robocopy \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\" \"$tmpProfile\\Default\" /E /R:2 /W:2 /NFL /NDL /NP 2>&1 | Out-String; Write-Host \"copy done\"; Test-Path \"$tmpProfile\\Default\\Network\\Cookies\"","timeout":30}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":26,"output":595,"cacheRead":92800,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":93421,"cost":{"input":0.0000036400000000000003,"output":0.0001666,"cacheRead":0.0025984,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.0027686399999999997}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779250285966,"responseId":"9b059780-1064-4a53-b7b5-ecfe8d5b44c9"}}
{"type":"message","id":"0835eeb9","parentId":"af8664d2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:11:35.624Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_8TOCfaBBn0B7OaJ1P9zV3717","toolName":"exec","content":[{"type":"text","text":"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n   ROBOCOPY     ::     Windows 的可靠文件复制                              \r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n  开始时间: 2026年5月20日 12:11:33\r\n        源: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\\r\n      目标: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_chrome_profile\\Default\\\r\n\r\n      文件: *.*\r\n\t    \r\n      选项: *.* /NDL /NFL /S /E /DCOPY:DA /COPY:DAT /NP /R:2 /W:2 \r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n                  总数        复制        跳过       不匹配        失败        其他\r\n       目录:       204       204         0         0         0         0\r\n       文件:      4269      4269         0         0         0         0\r\n       字节:  458.84 m  458.84 m         0         0         0         0\r\n       时间:   0:00:02   0:00:02                       0:00:00   0:00:00\r\n\r\n\r\n       速度:           233,558,245 字节/秒。\r\n       速度:            13,364.310 MB/分钟。\r\n   已结束: 2026年5月20日 12:11:35\r\n\r\n\r\ncopy done\nTrue"}],"details":{"status":"completed","exitCode":0,"durationMs":2335,"aggregated":"-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n   ROBOCOPY     ::     Windows 的可靠文件复制                              \r\n-------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n  开始时间: 2026年5月20日 12:11:33\r\n        源: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\Default\\\r\n      目标: C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\temp_chrome_profile\\Default\\\r\n\r\n      文件: *.*\r\n\t    \r\n      选项: *.* /NDL /NFL /S /E /DCOPY:DA /COPY:DAT /NP /R:2 /W:2 \r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n\r\n------------------------------------------------------------------------------\r\n\r\n                  总数        复制        跳过       不匹配        失败        其他\r\n       目录:       204       204         0         0         0         0\r\n       文件:      4269      4269         0         0         0         0\r\n       字节:  458.84 m  458.84 m         0         0         0         0\r\n       时间:   0:00:02   0:00:02                       0:00:00   0:00:00\r\n\r\n\r\n       速度:           233,558,245 字节/秒。\r\n       速度:            13,364.310 MB/分钟。\r\n   已结束: 2026年5月20日 12:11:35\r\n\r\n\r\ncopy done\nTrue","cwd":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace"},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779250295624}}
{"type":"message","id":"9613aa62","parentId":"0835eeb9","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:11:44.374Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me write a simple script using `launchPersistentContext` without `channel: 'chrome'` (using Playwright's bundled Chromium) to extract the cookies. This is the exact same approach that worked the first time.\n\nBut wait - the first successful run used this same approach and found 5 cookies. But then when I tried it later, it found 0 cookies. The difference might be:\n1. First run: used a copy of the profile RIGHT AFTER the user logged into TAPD\n2. Subsequent runs: used copies after I killed Chrome multiple times\n\nNow 周以天's session might still be in Chrome's database. Let me check: the `check_db.mjs` confirmed tapdsession is still there (1 row). So the session IS in the database.\n\nThe question is: will `launchPersistentContext` with a fresh copy of this profile work?\n\nLet me try it.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_01HHE8yjSO5uFdFIcJrm0723","name":"write","arguments":{"content":"/**\n * 用 Playwright 内置 Chromium 读取 temp profile 的 cookie（不指定 channel）\n */\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(fileURLToPath(import.meta.url));\nconst WS_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst TEMP_PROFILE = path.join(WS_DIR, 'temp_chrome_profile');\n\nasync function main() {\n  console.log('Launching persistent context (bundled Chromium)...');\n  \n  const context = await chromium.launchPersistentContext(TEMP_PROFILE, {\n    headless: false,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox'],\n  });\n\n  // 等 Chromium 完全初始化\n  await new Promise(r => setTimeout(r, 3000));\n\n  // 先读取已有 cookie（不导航）\n  let cookies = await context.cookies();\n  console.log(`Initial cookies: ${cookies.length}`);\n  \n  if (cookies.length > 0) {\n    const tapdCookies = cookies.filter(c => c.domain.includes('tapd.cn'));\n    console.log(`TAPD cookies: ${tapdCookies.length}`);\n    tapdCookies.forEach(c => {\n      console.log(`  ${c.name}: ${c.value.substring(0, 40)}`);\n    });\n  }\n\n  // 导航到 TAPD\n  const page = context.pages()[0] || await context.newPage();\n  console.log('\\nNavigating to TAPD...');\n  await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/bugtrace/bugs/add', {\n    waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n    timeout: 30000,\n  });\n  console.log('URL:', page.url());\n\n  if (page.url().includes('login')) {\n    console.log('⚠️ Login required');\n    // 等 60s 给人工登录\n    console.log('Waiting 60s for login...');\n    await page.waitForTimeout(60000);\n  }\n\n  // 获取最终 cookie\n  const finalCookies = await context.cookies();\n  const finalTapd = finalCookies.filter(c => c.domain.includes('tapd.cn'));\n  console.log(`\\nFinal TAPD cookies: ${finalTapd.length}`);\n  \n  if (finalTapd.length > 0) {\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(finalTapd, null, 2), 'utf8');\n    finalTapd.forEach(c => console.log(`  ${c.name}: ${c.value.substring(0, 40)}`));\n\n    const checks = ['tapdsession', 't_u', 't_cloud_login', '_t_crop', '_t_uid'];\n    for (const name of checks) {\n      const found = finalTapd.find(c => c.name === name);\n      console.log(`  ${name}: ${found ? '✅ ' + found.value.substring(0, 30) : '❌ NOT FOUND'}`);\n    }\n  }\n\n  await context.close();\n  try { fs.rmSync(TEMP_PROFILE, { recursive: true, force: true }); } catch {}\n}\n\nmain().catch(err => {\n  console.error('FAILED:', err.message);\n  process.exit(1);\n});\n","path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\extract_simple.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":454,"output":996,"cacheRead":93312,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":94762,"cost":{"input":0.00006356000000000001,"output":0.00027888,"cacheRead":0.002612736,"cacheWrite":0,"total"