{"type":"message","id":"c301feff","parentId":"e848d551","timestamp":"2026-05-20T04:15:16.377Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The session was invalid - the cookies we extracted don't work for logging into TAPD. This means the tapdsession we have is either:\n1. From a different user (叶枝君, not 周以天)\n2. Expired or invalidated\n\nI need to ask the user what they want to do. The Chrome v148 App Bound Encryption prevents direct cookie extraction. The session IS valid in Chrome's original profile (Chrome can use it), but I can't extract it.\n\nOptions:\n1. Open a Playwright browser window and let 周以天 log in fresh (via 微信扫码)\n2. User manually copies the cookies from Chrome DevTools\n3. We find another way\n\nLet me tell the user the situation.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"报告主人，情况是这样的：\n\n**挑战：** Chrome 148（当前版本）引入了 App Bound Encryption，cookie 被额外加密了一层绑定到 Chrome 进程本身，即使同一个 Windows 用户也无法直接解密的。\n\n**现状：**\n- ✅ 成功从数据库读取到 17 条 tapd 相关 cookie 记录\n- ✅ tapdsession 条目存在（expires 5/27）\n- ❌ **解密失败**（v20 新加密格式 + App Bound 保护）\n- ❌ 直接注入 cookie 测试 → 跳转到登录页（无效）\n\n**需要你帮忙：**\n我来打开一个 Playwright 浏览器窗口，让周以天扫码登录一下 TAPD，就能拿到完整 cookie 了。要现在开吗？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":106,"output":316,"cacheRead":106368,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":106790,"cost":{"input":0.00001484,"output":0.00008848,"cacheRead":0.0029783039999999998,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.003081624}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779250510993,"responseId":"00e4a2fe-7dc5-43e0-9260-22a38c767418"}}
