{"type":"message","id":"d956473e","parentId":"4e5f9ff4","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:19:10.255Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to:\n1. Keep both 叶枝君's and 周以天's TAPD cookies\n2. Both cookies need to be logged in daily to keep them alive\n\nCurrently the tapd_cookies.json has 周以天's cookies (14 cookies). I need to also save 叶枝君's previous cookies for backup, and set up the keepalive script to handle both.\n\nLet me think about the implementation:\n\n1. Current `tapd_cookies.json` → 周以天's cookies (just saved)\n2. I need 叶枝君's cookies too - but the previous ones were overwritten during my experiments. The user might need to export 叶枝君's cookies too.\n\nWait, actually the user said \"叶枝君的cookie\" - but the user IS 叶枝君. So the previous tapd_cookies.json that was working was 叶枝君's cookies. Those got overwritten.\n\nSo I need to:\n1. Ask the user to also export 叶枝君's cookies from Chrome (while logged in as 叶枝君)\n2. Save both sets of cookies in separate files\n3. Update the keepalive logic to handle both\n\nActually, thinking about this more, the keepalive script only needs one set of cookies to work. Since we use Playwright to navigate and the cookies keep the session alive, having the ability to use either set is enough.\n\nLet me think about the file organization:\n- `tapd_cookies.json` → main cookie file (currently 周以天, could be either)\n- `tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json` → 叶枝君's cookies\n- `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json` → 周以天's cookies (current)\n\nThen the keepalive script can rotate through them.\n\nBut the user hasn't exported 叶枝君's cookies yet. Let me:\n1. Save the current 周以天's cookies to a separate backup file\n2. Ask the user to also export 叶枝君's cookies\n3. Update TAPD keepalive\n\nActually, I should first save the current cookies as 周以天's backup, then ask for 叶枝君's export. Let me do this systematically.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白！我来管理好这两个账号的 cookie，每天保活。先备份当前的周以天 cookie，然后需要你也导出一份叶枝君的："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_nLSjfpf9Khv3Y88W3o1H5301","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_cookies.json\" \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json\" -Force; Write-Host \"周以天 cookie 已备份\""}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":4523,"output":615,"cacheRead":131584,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":136722,"cost":{"input":0.0006332200000000001,"output":0.0001722,"cacheRead":0.003684352,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004489772}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779257941719,"responseId":"b7044bde-8794-49b1-add8-16f24ce6349b"}}
