{"type":"message","id":"ae589bc4","parentId":"38fe8160","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:21:36.058Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user says to use 周以天's TAPD account for all future bug submissions. So:\n1. `tapd_cookies.json` stays as 周以天's cookies (which it currently is)\n2. I don't need 叶枝君's cookies for bug submission\n3. But the user mentioned \"每天都要登录一次保持活性\" for both cookies\n\nLet me clarify - does the user still want me to maintain 叶枝君's cookies as well for keepalive? Or just 周以天's?\n\nActually, the user said \"叶枝君的cookie和周以天的cookie都要管理好, 每天这两个cookie都要登录一次保持活性\" - they want both maintained. But for bug submission, use 周以天's.\n\nLet me:\n1. Keep `tapd_cookies.json` as the default (周以天's)\n2. Still ask for 叶枝君's cookies if they want both maintained\n3. Update the keepalive script to handle both\n\nBut actually, the user might not want to bother exporting 叶枝君's cookies now. Let me ask.\n\nNo wait, the user said \"后面开bug单都用周以天的tapd账号开单\" - this just clarifies which account to use for bug submission. They still mentioned both cookies need maintenance. But exporting 叶枝君's cookies requires the user to do it manually.\n\nLet me just confirm and set up the keepalive for 周以天's cookies first (since we already have them), and ask if they still want to export 叶枝君's.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"明白了！以后提单默认用周以天的账号。\n\n当前状态：\n- `tapd_cookies.json` ← 周以天的 ✅（提单用这个）\n- `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json` ← 备份 ✅\n\n那叶枝君的 cookie 还需要我维护保活吗？如果需要你也导一份给我，我两个都安排好保活；如果不需要，我就只保活周以天的～"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3815,"output":417,"cacheRead":133120,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":137352,"cost":{"input":0.0005341,"output":0.00011676000000000001,"cacheRead":0.00372736,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00437822}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779258089034,"responseId":"01e62e2b-201e-4c13-8006-7c0d055a150e"}}
