{"type":"message","id":"27feb63d","parentId":"583628b2","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:32.041Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now I need to update the keepalive script to handle both cookies. Let me check the current keepalive script:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"两个 cookie 都存好了！现在更新保活脚本，每天轮流给两个账号续命："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_NcPVJTRoIf4X9iKNshV67721","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":106,"output":113,"cacheRead":141696,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":141915,"cost":{"input":0.00001484,"output":0.00003164,"cacheRead":0.003967488,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004013968}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779258209742,"responseId":"7c9d8c45-4d01-473f-a511-d4e297ec1d71"}}
{"type":"message","id":"5514f6fe","parentId":"27feb63d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:32.051Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_NcPVJTRoIf4X9iKNshV67721","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"// TAPD Keepalive Script\n// Loads cookies, hits the workspace dashboard to refresh server-side session,\n// then saves the new cookies back to tapd_cookies.json.\n// Run periodically (every 1-2 days) to keep login alive indefinitely.\n//\n// Exit codes:\n//   0 = success (cookies refreshed)\n//   1 = cookie invalid / login expired (need re-login)\n//   2 = script error (network, etc.)\n\nimport { chromium } from 'playwright';\nimport fs from 'fs';\nimport path from 'path';\nimport { fileURLToPath } from 'url';\n\nconst __filename = fileURLToPath(import.meta.url);\nconst __dirname = path.dirname(__filename);\nconst WORKSPACE_DIR = path.resolve(__dirname, '..');\nconst COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_storage.json');\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'tapd-keepalive-state.json');\n\nconst STEALTH_INIT = () => {\n  delete navigator.webdriver;\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'webdriver', { get: () => false });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'plugins', { get: () => [1, 2, 3, 4, 5] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'languages', { get: () => ['zh-CN', 'zh'] });\n  Object.defineProperty(navigator, 'hardwareConcurrency', { get: () => 8 });\n  window.chrome = { runtime: {}, loadTimes: function () {}, csi: function () {}, app: {} };\n};\n\nfunction log(msg) {\n  console.log(`[${new Date().toISOString()}] ${msg}`);\n}\n\nfunction writeState(state) {\n  try {\n    fs.mkdirSync(path.dirname(STATE_FILE), { recursive: true });\n    fs.writeFileSync(STATE_FILE, JSON.stringify(state, null, 2));\n  } catch (e) {\n    console.error('Failed to write state:', e.message);\n  }\n}\n\nasync function main() {\n  if (!fs.existsSync(COOKIES_FILE)) {\n    log(`ERROR: cookies file not found: ${COOKIES_FILE}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: 'cookies_missing', at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    process.exit(1);\n  }\n\n  const oldCookies = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, 'utf8'));\n  log(`Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);\n\n  const browser = await chromium.launch({\n    headless: true,\n    args: ['--no-sandbox', '--disable-blink-features=AutomationControlled'],\n  });\n  const ctx = await browser.newContext({\n    locale: 'zh-CN',\n    viewport: { width: 1920, height: 1080 },\n    userAgent: 'Mozilla/5.0 (Windows NT 10.0; Win64; x64) AppleWebKit/537.36 (KHTML, like Gecko) Chrome/125.0.0.0 Safari/537.36',\n  });\n  await ctx.addCookies(oldCookies);\n  const page = await ctx.newPage();\n  await page.addInitScript(STEALTH_INIT);\n\n  try {\n    log('Visiting workspace dashboard...');\n    const resp = await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/31253609/', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    });\n    await page.waitForTimeout(3000);\n\n    const url = page.url();\n    const title = await page.title();\n    const status = resp?.status();\n    log(`HTTP ${status} | url=${url} | title=${title}`);\n\n    if (url.includes('login') || title.includes('登录') || title.includes('WAF')) {\n      log('❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login');\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);\n    }\n\n    // Bonus: also poke story-list to make sure deep nav still works\n    await page.goto('https://www.tapd.cn/tapd_fe/31253609/story/list', {\n      waitUntil: 'domcontentloaded',\n      timeout: 30000,\n    }).catch(() => {});\n    await page.waitForTimeout(2000);\n\n    // Save refreshed cookies\n    const newCookies = await ctx.cookies();\n    const newStorage = await ctx.storageState();\n\n    fs.writeFileSync(COOKIES_FILE, JSON.stringify(newCookies, null, 2));\n    fs.writeFileSync(STORAGE_FILE, JSON.stringify(newStorage, null, 2));\n\n    // Find tapdsession expiry for state\n    const tapdsession = newCookies.find((c) => c.name === 'tapdsession');\n    const exp = tapdsession?.expires > 0\n      ? new Date(tapdsession.expires * 1000).toISOString()\n      : 'session';\n\n    log(`✅ Refreshed ${newCookies.length} cookies | tapdsession exp: ${exp}`);\n    writeState({\n      ok: true,\n      at: new Date().toISOString(),\n      cookieCount: newCookies.length,\n      tapdsessionExpires: exp,\n      title,\n    });\n\n    await browser.close();\n    process.exit(0);\n  } catch (e) {\n    log(`ERROR: ${e.message}`);\n    writeState({ ok: false, error: e.message, at: new Date().toISOString() });\n    try { await browser.close(); } catch {}\n    process.exit(2);\n  }\n}\n\nmain();\n"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779258212051}}
{"type":"message","id":"d200692d","parentId":"5514f6fe","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:36.187Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The current keepalive script only handles one cookie file (`tapd_cookies.json`). I need to update it to handle both 叶枝君 and 周以天's cookies. I'll update the script to:\n\n1. Accept a parameter for which account to keep alive\n2. Or handle both accounts sequentially\n\nLet me update the keepalive script to be parameterized, supporting both accounts. I'll also set up the heartbeat config to run keepalive for both accounts.\n\nActually, let me think about the simplest approach. The keepalive script currently reads `tapd_cookies.json`. I can:\n\n1. Modify the keepalive script to accept a cookie file path argument\n2. Create a wrapper that runs keepalive for both accounts\n3. The main `tapd_cookies.json` stays as 周以天 (for bug submission)\n\nLet me update the keepalive script to support parameters.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Vl90H3S8frhgxIBYyMX45610","name":"read","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md","limit":10,"offset":1}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":1379,"output":286,"cacheRead":141824,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143489,"cost":{"input":0.00019306000000000003,"output":0.00008008,"cacheRead":0.003971072,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004244212}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779258212054,"responseId":"54b67ec0-80e8-48c7-9c62-24899ad7e95c"}}
{"type":"message","id":"b62ddd54","parentId":"d200692d","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:36.193Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_Vl90H3S8frhgxIBYyMX45610","toolName":"read","content":[{"type":"text","text":"# Heartbeat Tasks\n\n## 登录保活（每天一次）\n\n每天检查保活状态文件，如果距离上次执行 > 20 小时则自动执行。\n\n### TAPD 保活\n\n- 状态文件：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state.json`\n- 脚本：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n\n[18 more lines in file. Use offset=11 to continue.]"}],"isError":false,"timestamp":1779258216193}}
{"type":"message","id":"a4251527","parentId":"b62ddd54","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:41.713Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now let me update the keepalive script to support both accounts. The simplest approach: modify the script to accept an optional parameter for the cookie file, and create a wrapper that runs for both accounts.\n\nActually, let me just update the keepalive script to handle both accounts by default. It will:\n1. Keep alive 周以天 (default, `tapd_cookies.json` stays as the main working copy)\n2. Also keep alive 叶枝君\n\nAnd update the heartbeat config to check both state files.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_mdmBsJDPukbGJky1BafK7290","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Copy-Item \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\AppData\\Local\\Google\\Chrome\\User Data\\tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json\" -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue; Write-Host \"checking...\"\nnode -e \"const fs=require('fs'); const f=['tapd_cookies.json','tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json','tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json']; f.forEach(fn => { const p='C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\'+fn; if(fs.existsSync(p)) { const c=JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync(p)); const s=c.find(x=>x.name==='tapdsession'); console.log(fn+': '+c.length+' cookies, tapdsession='+(s?s.value.substring(0,20):'MISSING')); }});\"","timeout":5}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":103,"output":356,"cacheRead":143488,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":143947,"cost":{"input":0.000014420000000000001,"output":0.00009968000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004017664,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004131764}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779258216196,"responseId":"49ac02c0-5cea-4b78-87d9-09db2c017d37"}}
