{"type":"message","id":"e49d884b","parentId":"8340caf8","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:23:50.673Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Three cookie files:\n1. `tapd_cookies.json` → 周以天 (14 cookies) - 主文件，提单用\n2. `tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json` → 叶枝君 (17 cookies)\n3. `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json` → 周以天备份 (14 cookies)\n\nNow I need to update the keepalive script to handle both accounts. Let me modify it to accept a parameter for which cookie file to use, and create a wrapper.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_Afob8y6N7nyIQymprHR40348","name":"edit","arguments":{"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\scripts\\tapd_keepalive.mjs","edits":[{"oldText":"const COOKIES_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_storage.json');\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', 'tapd-keepalive-state.json');","newText":"// 支持传入参数指定账号：'zhouyitian'（默认）或 'yezhijun'\nconst ACCOUNT = process.argv[2] || 'zhouyitian';\nconst ACCOUNT_LABELS = { zhouyitian: '周以天', yezhijun: '叶枝君' };\nconst label = ACCOUNT_LABELS[ACCOUNT] || ACCOUNT;\n\nconst COOKIES_FILE = ACCOUNT === 'yezhijun'\n  ? path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json')\n  : path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json');\nconst STORAGE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, `tapd_storage_${ACCOUNT}.json`);\nconst STATE_FILE = path.join(WORKSPACE_DIR, 'memory', `tapd-keepalive-state-${ACCOUNT}.json`);"},{"oldText":"  log(`Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);","newText":"  log(`[${label}] Loaded ${oldCookies.length} cookies`);"},{"oldText":"    log('❌ Session EXPIRED - need re-login');\n      writeState({\n        ok: false,\n        error: 'session_expired',\n        at: new Date().toISOString(),\n        finalUrl: url,\n        title,\n      });\n      await browser.close();\n      process.exit(1);","newText":"    log(`[${label}] Session EXPIRED - need re-login`