{"type":"message","id":"9363e141","parentId":"6a7eabf7","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:24:09.583Z","message":{"role":"toolResult","toolCallId":"call_00_DzhLrgSS9gDOWXgF2VuL8634","toolName":"edit","content":[{"type":"text","text":"Successfully replaced 1 block(s) in C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\HEARTBEAT.md."}],"details":{"diff":"    ...\n  3 ## 登录保活（每天一次）\n  4 \n  5 每天检查保活状态文件，如果距离上次执行 > 20 小时则自动执行。\n  6 \n- 7 ### TAPD 保活\n+ 7 ### TAPD 保活（双账号）\n  8 \n- 9 - 状态文件：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state.json`\n-10 - 脚本：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n+ 9 - 周以天（提单用）：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（默认）\n+10   - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n+11   - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-zhouyitian.json`\n+12 - 叶枝君：`node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\n+13   - Cookie：`tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n+14   - 状态：`memory/tapd-keepalive-state-yezhijun.json`\n+15 - 两个账号每天都要跑一次保活\n 11 - 退出码：\n 12   - `0` → ✅ 成功续期\n 13   - `1` → ❌ 需要重新扫码登录 TAPD，**主动通知主人**\n 14   - `2` → ⚠️ 脚本错误，记录到当天 memory 文件\n    ...","firstChangedLine":7},"isError":false,"timestamp":1779258249583}}
{"type":"message","id":"75ec7875","parentId":"9363e141","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:24:16.884Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Now update MEMORY.md to record this configuration:","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_FZKlyIjm4kuiuq4x07748192","name":"edit","arguments":{"edits":[{"oldText":"## TAPD 登录保活方案（2026-05-18）\n\n- **保活脚本：** `workspace/scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n- **原理：** 每天 headless 访问一次 workspace 主页，TAPD 会自动续 `tapdsession` 7 天\n- **状态文件：** `workspace/memory/tapd-keepalive-state.json`（记录上次执行结果）\n- **HEARTBEAT 集成：** `HEARTBEAT.md` 已配置，每天自动跑一次\n- **退出码：** 0=成功续期 / 1=登录失效需扫码 / 2=脚本错误\n- **失效救援：** 检测到 cookie 失效时，用 `headless: false` 跑 `chromium.launch`，访问 `https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login`，点微信扫码，让主人扫一下，然后保存新 cookie\n- **关键 cookie：** `tapdsession`(7天)、`t_u`、`t_cloud_login`、`_t_crop`、`_t_uid`","newText":"## TAPD 登录保活方案（2026-05-20 更新：双账号）\n\n### 两个账号\n- **周以天**：提单用，cookie `tapd_cookies_zhouyitian.json`\n- **叶枝君**：备用，cookie `tapd_cookies_yezhijun.json`\n- 主文件 `tapd_cookies.json` 保持为周以天（提单脚本默认读取）\n\n### 保活脚本\n- **保活脚本：** `workspace/scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`\n- **用法：** `node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs`（默认周以天）/ `node scripts/tapd_keepalive.mjs yezhijun`\n- **原理：** 每天 headless 访问一次 workspace 主页，TAPD 会自动续 `tapdsession` 7 天\n- **状态文件：** `memory/tapd-keepalive-state-zhouyitian.json` / `memory/tapd-keepalive-state-yezhijun.json`\n- **HEARTBEAT 集成：** `HEARTBEAT.md` 已配置，每天两个账号都要跑一次\n- **退出码：** 0=成功续期 / 1=登录失效需扫码 / 2=脚本错误\n- **失效救援：** 检测到 cookie 失效时，用 `headless: false` 跑 Playwright，访问 `https://www.tapd.cn/cloud_logins/login`，点微信扫码，让主人扫一下，然后保存新 cookie\n- **关键 cookie：** `tapdsession`(7天)、`t_u`、`t_cloud_login`、`_t_crop`、`_t_uid`"}],"path":"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\workspace\\MEMORY.md"}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":43,"output":760,"cacheRead":147712,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":148515,"cost":{"input":0.00000602000000000000