{"type":"message","id":"a559d4ed","parentId":"351954dd","timestamp":"2026-05-20T06:56:05.558Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to set the HFS password to \"111111\". HFS v3 uses SRP, so I can't just put a plaintext password in the config. I need to generate the SRP verifier for \"111111\" and replace it in the config.\n\nHowever, generating an SRP verifier requires knowledge of the SRP protocol parameters (N, g) and the hashing algorithm. HFS v3 uses specific SRP parameters.\n\nAlternative approaches:\n1. Use HFS's CLI to change the password\n2. Remove the password entirely from config\n3. Write a script to generate the SRP verifier\n\nActually, the simplest approach is to use HFS's own CLI. HFS v3 supports `hfs.exe --cli` which opens a command-line interface where you can run `passwd admin` to set a new password. But this requires interactive input.\n\nActually, there's a better approach. I can kill HFS, modify the config to remove the password (delete the SRP line), restart HFS, then set the password from the HFS web interface.\n\nOr even simpler: I can use the HFS command to change the password non-interactively. Let me check if HFS supports piping the password.\n\nActually, let me just try the simplest approach: modify the config to remove the SRP field (which removes password protection), then the user can set a new password through the web interface.\n\nWait, but HFS v3 stores the SRP verifier. To set a new password, I need to:\n1. Either use HFS's own mechanism to generate the SRP verifier\n2. Or delete the account and recreate\n\nThe simplest approach: I know HFS v3 has a CLI that accepts commands. Let me try piping to it.\n\nActually, let me try another approach. I can use the HFS API to set the password. HFS v3 has a REST API. Or I can use the `hfs.exe set-password` command if it exists.\n\nLet me first check what CLI commands HFS supports.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好，我来重置。HFS 的密码是 SRP 加密的，得用它的命令来改："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_CIzq7PXBsEnEd85M8Z2k8862","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Stop-Process -Id 35000 -Force; Start-Sleep -Seconds 2; Write-Host \"HFS stopped\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3944,"output":536,"cacheRead":152576,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":157056,"cost":{"input":0.00055216,"output":0.00015008,"cacheRead":0.004272128,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004974368}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779260157344,"responseId":"56512651-13d7-4da6-9ed5-52dd051b8f19"}}
