{"type":"message","id":"8c24f44f","parentId":"2dcf900c","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:30:08.256Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"Port 80 is not shown as listening by netstat. But now HFS on port 8000 shows the correct VFS structure. The issue is clear:\n\n1. HFS is now running on port **8000** (not 80 as before)\n2. The resource URL path shows `cdn_solo` is a subfolder: files are at `/cdn_solo/Version/xxx`, not `/Version/xxx`\n\nWait, but looking at the HFS v3 Web UI:\n```\n<ul>\n<li><a href='cdn_solo/'>cdn_solo/</a>\n</ul>\n```\n\nThis means the root shows `cdn_solo/` as a VFS child. To access version files, the URL would be `http://IP:8000/cdn_solo/Version/version_xxx.bytes`. \n\nLet me try this URL.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_bCXONfLwHf2ezJmSRNtD2413","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查实际的文件访问路径\ncurl.exe -s -o NUL -w \"%{http_code}\" http://127.0.0.1:8000/cdn_solo/Version/version_20260312.bytes 2>&1; Write-Host \" <- /cdn_solo/Version/...\"; curl.exe -s -o NUL -w \"%{http_code}\" http://127.0.0.1:8000/cdn_solo/ 2>&1; Write-Host \" <- /cdn_solo/\"; # 看看原来的 hfs 快捷方式指向\nGet-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\Desktop\\hfs.lnk\" -Encoding UTF8 2>&1 | Select-Object -First 5","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":69,"output":399,"cacheRead":173568,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":174036,"cost":{"input":0.00000966,"output":0.00011172000000000001,"cacheRead":0.004859904,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.004981284}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779262201351,"responseId":"344fbf39-7d6e-41db-86aa-8537b1b0f24c"}}
