{"type":"message","id":"3c1a0633","parentId":"7e31962b","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:30:20.596Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"OK, so:\n- `http://127.0.0.1:8000/cdn_solo/Version/version_20260312.bytes` → 200 ✅ The file IS accessible via the `/cdn_solo/` prefix!\n- `http://127.0.0.1:8000/` → 200 ✅ (shows the root directory listing with `cdn_solo/` link)\n\nSo the issue is:\n1. **HFS moved from port 80 to port 8000** - the original port 80 is no longer serving\n2. **VFS path changed** - files are now under `/cdn_solo/` subpath instead of being served directly from root\n\nThe original HFS (before I killed it) was probably configured differently. The original config had the same VFS structure, but the old HFS process (PID 35000) had been running since before and might have had additional settings.\n\nWait, actually looking at the config more carefully, the original config DID have `cdn_solo` as a child. But maybe the original HFS was configured differently through the web UI at some point and saved additional VFS settings. When I overwrote the config, those customizations were lost.\n\nBut actually, the more likely issue is simpler:\n1. Before my changes, HFS was on port 80 (served by the original process 35000)\n2. I killed it and modified config.yaml\n3. I started a new HFS which couldn't use port 80 (something else was using it briefly, or it was still in TIME_WAIT)\n4. The new HFS fell back to port 8000\n\nThe real fix: kill both HFS instances, wait for port 80 to be free, then start fresh.\n\nActually, looking again at the process list - PID 32904 tried port 80 but failed (\"http port 80 busy\") which means something ELSE was using port 80 at that time. This could have been the old HFS process that wasn't fully killed.\n\nLet me kill both HFS instances and restart cleanly on port 80.\n\nBut there's also the VFS path issue. Let me check if the original HFS also required `/cdn_solo/` prefix or if it served files directly from root.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"找到了 **两个问题**：\n\n1️⃣ **端口变了**：之前 HFS 在 80 端口，现在跑在 8000（我启动时 80 被占了）\n2️⃣ **访问路径**：文件在 `/cdn_solo/` 子路径下，不是根目录\n\n让我恢复原样："},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_xefZpPmHUYcP3PuZT7cs2743","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"Get-Process hfs -ErrorAction SilentlyContinue | Stop-Process -Force; Start-Sleep -Seconds 5; Write-Host \"killed\"; netstat -ano | Select-String \":80 \" | Select-String \"LISTEN\" 2>&1","timeout":15}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":433,"output":659,"cacheRead":173952,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":175044,"cost":{"input":0.000060620000000000006,"output":0.00018452,"cacheRead":0.004870656,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005115796000000001}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779262208790,"responseId":"1082dd43-90c7-43ef-90e5-e034292ad7c9"}}
