{"type":"message","id":"0a3389df","parentId":"f0e90cfd","timestamp":"2026-05-20T07:59:28.304Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to set DeepSeek as the default model. I need to update the OpenClaw configuration to use DeepSeek as the default model. Let me check how to do this.\n\nI can use the `gateway` tool to update the config, or I can edit the config file directly. Let me check the config schema first.\n\nActually, the session_status tool showed that the model can be changed per-session. For a permanent default, I need to update the OpenClaw configuration.\n\nLet me check the gateway config.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我把默认模型切到 DeepSeek～"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_ZXIQ3LxzpxPe6kprX5bu2712","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"type \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\" | node -e \"\nconst fs = require('fs');\nconst config = JSON.parse(fs.readFileSync('/dev/stdin', 'utf8'));\n// Look for model-related settings\nconst keys = Object.keys(config).filter(k => k.toLowerCase().includes('model') || k.toLowerCase().includes('default'));\nconsole.log('Model-related keys:', keys);\n\" 2>&1; Write-Host \"---\"; Get-Content \"C:\\Users\\yyzypublic\\.openclaw\\openclaw.json\" -Encoding UTF8 | Select-Object -First 5","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":13246,"output":317,"cacheRead":163840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":177403,"cost":{"input":0.0018544400000000002,"output":0.00008876000000000001,"cacheRead":0.0045875199999999994,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006530719999999999}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779263963444,"responseId":"9e5c0e60-f82a-48d4-8152-f2ced69024e7"}}
