{"type":"message","id":"25191d4b","parentId":"5a9d6ef3","timestamp":"2026-05-20T08:02:15.739Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user asked to see the skill list. Let me present it clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"安装的技能如下：\n\n**🤖 核心技能**\n- `feishu-doc` — 飞书文档读写\n- `feishu-drive` — 飞书云盘管理\n- `feishu-perm` — 飞书权限管理\n- `feishu-wiki` — 飞书知识库\n- `tapd-bug-create` — TAPD 自动提单\n- `update-server` — 服务端 DevOps 更新\n- `memory-keeper` — 记忆管理\n- `skill-creator` — 创建/编辑技能\n- `taskflow` — 多步骤任务编排\n- `taskflow-inbox-triage` — 收件箱分流\n\n**🛠️ 开发工具**\n- `coding-agent` — 编码助手\n- `github` — GitHub 操作\n- `gh-issues` — GitHub Issues\n- `node-connect` — Node 连接\n\n**💬 通讯**\n- `discord` — Discord 集成\n- `slack` — Slack 集成\n- `bluebubbles` — iMessage\n- `imsg` — iMessage\n\n**🎨 创意/媒体**\n- `sag` — ElevenLabs TTS 语音\n- `sherpa-onnx-tts` — 离线 TTS\n- `voice-call` — 语音通话\n- `openai-whisper` / `openai-whisper-api` — 语音识别\n- `gemini` — Gemini 视觉\n- `video-frames` — 视频帧提取\n- `songsee` / `spotify-player` / `sonoscli` — 音乐\n- `gifgrep` — GIF 搜索\n- `nano-pdf` — PDF 处理\n\n**📝 笔记**\n- `notion` — Notion\n- `obsidian` — Obsidian\n- `bear-notes` — Bear\n- `apple-notes` / `apple-reminders` — Apple 备忘录/提醒\n\n**🔐 安全**\n- `1password` — 1Password\n- `oracle` — Oracle\n\n**🌐 其他**\n- `weather` — 天气\n- `goplaces` — 位置\n- `canvas` — Canvas LMS\n- `trello` — Trello\n- `clawhub` — 技能市场\n- `blogwatcher` — 博客监控\n- `healthcheck` — 健康检查\n- `model-usage` — 模型用量\n- `tmux` — Tmux\n- `camsnap` — 摄像头快照\n- `openhue` — 智能灯控\n- `xurl` — URL 工具\n- `session-logs` — Session 日志\n- `summarize` — 摘要\n\n装了 **59 个技能**，不过大部分要配过才能用～常用的主要是 TAPD 提单、飞书文档、服务端更新这几个 🎯"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":380,"output":664,"cacheRead":187136,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":188180,"cost":{"input":0.000053200000000000006,"output":0.00018592,"cacheRead":0.0052398079999999994,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.005478927999999