{"type":"message","id":"687534df","parentId":"09489b7a","timestamp":"2026-05-20T08:03:03.111Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to create a story/requirement (需求单) in TAPD for the client team. Let me check the tapd-bug-create skill for how to create a story, since it has story creation functionality.\n\nFrom the skill file I read earlier, there's a `createStory` function:\n\n```javascript\nimport { createStory } from './scripts/create_story.mjs';\nawait createStory({ title: '需求标题' }); // 默认客户端模板\nawait createStory({ title: '需求标题', template: 'server' }); // 服务端模板\n```\n\nSince the user said \"给客户端\", I should use the `client` template (客户端开单).\n\nBut the user didn't give me a specific title or description. Let me ask for more details, or if this is just a test, I can use a generic title.\n\nActually, looking at the conversation context, the user just said \"提个需求单给客户端\" without more details. This might be a test or they might expect me to ask for the title. Let me ask.\n\nWait, actually the user is testing me. Let me ask what the requirement is about.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，提需求单需要知道需求标题和内容，这个需求单是做什么的呀？"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":24370,"output":262,"cacheRead":163840,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":188472,"cost":{"input":0.0034118000000000004,"output":0.00007336,"cacheRead":0.0045875199999999994,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.00807268}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779264177772,"responseId":"4cd35946-f982-4a2e-8b62-6bcd971d42ea"}}
