{"type":"message","id":"5eb6f668","parentId":"a748bd08","timestamp":"2026-05-20T08:49:19.878Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants to see the 6 templates for creating 1V1 stories. I have this information in the TAPD skill. Let me present it clearly.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"**1V1 需求单 6 种模板**\n\n| 模板 | 适用 | 预设子工作项 | 默认处理人 |\n|------|------|-------------|-----------|\n| **client** 🖥️ | 客户端开单 | 客户端[12] + 策划[14] + QA[16] | 叶枝君 |\n| **server** ⚙️ | 服务端开单 | 服务端[13] + 策划[14] + QA[16] | 陈霄豪 |\n| **design** 📐 | 策划需求单 | 策划[14] + QA[16] | 赵乾 |\n| **ui** 🎨 | UI需求单 | UI[7] + UI验收[8] + 客户端[12] + 策划[14] + QA[16] | 小冰 |\n| **motion** 💫 | 动作需求单 | 2D动作[2] + 3D动作[3] + 动效[9] + 动效验收[10] + 策划[14] + QA[16] | 肖和 |\n| **audio** 🎵 | 音频需求单 | 音频[11] + 策划[14] + QA[16] | 吴美霞 |\n\n**用法示例：**\n```javascript\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'client' })  // 客户端需求\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'server' })  // 服务端需求\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'design' })  // 策划需求\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'ui' })      // UI需求\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'motion' })  // 动作需求\ncreateStory({ title: 'xxx', template: 'audio' })   // 音频需求\n```"}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":3125,"output":444,"cacheRead":198016,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":201585,"cost":{"input":0.0004375,"output":0.00012432,"cacheRead":0.0055444479999999996,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.006106268}},"stopReason":"stop","timestamp":1779266954777,"responseId":"a2a0b2f9-8ff6-4994-87f8-cc74a5227639"}}
