{"type":"message","id":"4e2311fc","parentId":"1f1081ec","timestamp":"2026-05-20T08:59:56.669Z","message":{"role":"assistant","content":[{"type":"thinking","thinking":"The user wants me to save the current skill and memory state. Let me review what's been updated in this session and make sure everything is properly saved.\n\nKey changes this session:\n1. TAPD cookie management - dual accounts (叶枝君 + 周以天)\n2. TAPD keepalive script updated for dual accounts\n3. Template configuration updated (UI去掉客户端, motion去掉3D动作/动效/动效验收)\n4. Default model changed to DeepSeek\n5. HFS password reset and port issue fixed\n6. New understanding: 提需求单 = 1V1需求单, 用叶枝君账号\n7. 提单bug用周以天账号\n8. Git commit log query done\n\nLet me check the current state of MEMORY.md and TOOLS.md to make sure everything's captured.","thinkingSignature":"reasoning_content"},{"type":"text","text":"好的，我来检查这轮 session 的所有变更，确保都存好了～"},{"type":"toolCall","id":"call_00_DteLBxQjGKZbZfOS0CMT5519","name":"exec","arguments":{"command":"# 检查关键文件有没有记录到\nnode -e \"\nconst fs=require('fs');\n\nconst files = [\n  'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\MEMORY.md',\n  'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\workspace\\\\HEARTBEAT.md',\n  'C:\\\\Users\\\\yyzypublic\\\\.openclaw\\\\plugin-skills\\\\tapd-bug-create\\\\SKILL.md',\n];\n\nconst checks = [\n  '双账号',\n  '需求单 = 1V1 需求单',\n  'UI验收',\n  '3D动作',\n  '动效',\n  'deepseek-v4-flash',\n];\n\nfor (const f of files) {\n  const content = fs.readFileSync(f, 'utf8');\n  for (const c of checks) {\n    const found = content.includes(c);\n    if (found) console.log('✅', f.split('\\\\\\\\').pop(), '→', c);\n  }\n}\n\"","timeout":10}}],"api":"openai-completions","provider":"deepseek","model":"deepseek-v4-flash","usage":{"input":11643,"output":468,"cacheRead":196608,"cacheWrite":0,"totalTokens":208719,"cost":{"input":0.00163002,"output":0.00013104000000000002,"cacheRead":0.005505024,"cacheWrite":0,"total":0.007266084}},"stopReason":"toolUse","timestamp":1779267589311,"respons